            "title": "盤中速報 - 聯德控股-KY(4912)股價拉至漲停，漲停價102.5元，成交1,826張",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>聯德控股-KY(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:4912:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/4912\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">4912-TW</a>)22日09:43上漲8.9元，股價漲停報102.5元，委買11張、委賣83張，成交1,826張。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>主要業務為精密金屬模具設計及生產。五金沖壓件生產。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>聯德控股-KY(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:4912:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/4912\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">4912-TW</a>)近5日股價上漲2.52%，集中市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>上漲0.98%，股價漲幅表現優於大盤。</p></section><section><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：-1,315 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：-1,411 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：+125 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：-29 張</li> <li>融資增減：+109 張</li> <li>融券增減：+1 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
